    {
      "chinese": "來吧！虹谷媽媽，爸爸賜下飾品。瀑布的聲音，斧頭劈柴的聲音。Hadul射老鷹，貪吃的Landiq配飯吃。被Ma’ia搶走，Ma’ia一直搶著。反被Pailung搶走，一直反被Pailung搶著。病中的女人，腰頂背物，手環的響聲。\r\n",
      "ab": "Nuin Tina hungku, aivan tama bainkin. Cius cius tastas, paqting paqting tunpu’. Manaq Hadul quic, quic Landiq nguzuc. Siqalavun Ma’ia, Ma’ia siqaqalavan. Siqungunun Pailung, Pailung siqungunun. Halang tu binau’az, pa’av tu inama, pasling tu bistunan.",
